Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or inconclusive
Control measures
Measures applied: Quarantine, Screening, Vaccination prohibited, No treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: No other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type:
1. Veterinary Faculty in Sarajevo (National laboratory)
